long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Calendar.com provides the best solution to schedule meetings and avoid double bookings. By integrating with your calendar, this tool automates the meeting scheduling process. Whether you use the free or paid version of Calendar.com, you can benefit from the Calendar.com Chrome extension.

The Chrome extension provides the following features:
- Access all your time slots and scheduling links from anywhere on the web.
- Copy and share your scheduling links.
- Quickly select and add available times to emails.

ABOUT CALENDAR.COM

Calendar.com simplifies the process of meeting with people anywhere by syncing with both personal and business calendars and eliminating the need for back-and-forth emails.
